fields.name: MV Beanie Hat
fields.description:
Minimal form, maximum presence. The MV Beanie strips it back to the essentials—clean lines, rich texture, and a flawless fit—letting quality and attitude do the talking. Crafted from soft-touch knit fabric and finished with our signature MV embroidery, it’s a cold-weather staple with year-round energy.

Whether pulled low for anonymity or pushed back for effortless cool, this beanie is made for those who carry confidence in silence.
Made for movers, makers, and modern-day menaces. No frills. Just presence.
details: Soft-touch knit for warmth and comfort

fields.name: MV Fur Bucket Hat
fields.description:
A bold reinterpretation of retro cool, the MV Furry Bucket Hat fuses vintage edge with modern extravagance. Cloaked in ultra-soft plush fur, this piece transforms a nostalgic silhouette into a statement of luxury. With every glance, texture, and detail, it speaks volumes—of confidence, of rebellion, of refined streetwear made for those who lead, not follow.

The MV insignia is subtly embroidered into the fabric—an understated salute to heritage, a powerful symbol of the Menace ethos. Whether you're layering for winter city strolls or pushing boundaries at late-night gatherings, this bucket hat demands attention without saying a word.More than a hat—it's a mindset. For those who don’t just wear fashion, but own it.
details: Luxe faux fur exterior for maximum tactile appeal
Classic bucket hat silhouette reimagined for a modern fit
Comfortable inner lining for all-day wear

fields.name: MV Denim Bucket Hat
fields.description:
Timeless denim, unapologetically redefined. The MV Denim Bucket Hat is where classic streetwear meets elevated rebellion. Crafted from premium-washed denim, this piece merges grit with polish—an effortless staple that nods to 90s attitude while carving out space in today’s fashion-forward rotation.

Finished with subtle MV embroidery and a structured brim, it’s built for those who move between worlds—city grit, studio sessions, front-row energy. This isn’t just denim; it’s denim with purpose.
A piece for the fearless. For those who turn basics into statements, and moments into movements.
details: Classic bucket hat shape with modern proportions
Soft inner lining for elevated comfort

fields.name: MV Fur Cap
fields.description:
A statement of modern opulence, the MV Fur Cap redefines streetwear through the lens of luxury. Crafted with an ultra-soft fur texture that invites touch and turns heads, this cap elevates the everyday into the extraordinary. The MV signature branding is seamlessly integrated into the design a subtle nod to heritage, a bold declaration of being a Menace.

Whether paired with oversized outerwear or sleek tailoring, the MV Fur Cap blurs the line between cozy and couture. Designed not just to be worn, but to be seen.An essential for those who move with confidence, dress with intent and never settle for the ordinary.
details: Adjustable back strap for a custom feel

fields.name: MV Block Frame Sunglasses
fields.description:
Sharp angles. Sharper intent. The MV Block Sunglasses are a study in controlled boldness—where brutalist design meets modern-day defiance. With a chunky rectangular silhouette and precision-cut edges, Block doesn’t just frame the face—it defines the look.

Built to disrupt, not disappear, these sunglasses are a visual shield for the unapologetic. The MV logo is laser-etched with subtle precision, marking each pair with quiet authority.For those who don’t just walk the line—they draw their own.
details: Durable acetate construction with a premium hand-feel
UV-protective lenses with subtle tint options
Laser-etched MV logo on the arm
Comes with a branded protective case

fields.name: MV Slice Frame Sunglasses
fields.description:
Cut sharp. Worn smooth. The MV Slice Sunglasses bring sleek precision to the everyday, with a streamlined oval frame that glides between retro influence and modern edge. Lightweight yet assertive, Slice is built for those who move clean, think fast, and dress with intent.

Every curve is considered. Every detail refined. The MV logo is etched with subtle force—a quiet flex for those who know. Slice is not just eyewear—it’s a signal. For visionaries only.
details: Slim oval frame design with a futuristic-meets-vintage feel
Lightweight acetate for effortless all-day wear
UV-protective lenses with a clean, tonal finish
Laser-etched MV branding on the temple
Comes with a branded protective case
